Fit & style

  • Slip-on sandals make a casual summer staple
  • Plastic construction with allover single color for a sharp look
  • Open toe and back offer a breezy fit to keep feet cool
  • Great for gardening, errands or simply hanging in your yard

Specifications

Description

Update your summer wardrobe with the cool and casual look of these comfy Neida EVA Two-Band Slide Sandals from Shade & Shore™. These simple yet stylish slip-on sandals feature 100% plastic construction for a squishy feel underfoot and a surface that easily wipes clean. Great for wearing in your garden, on your deck or even to the pool, these open-toe sandals feature a double band on top with two buckles, all in a single color for a chic twist on a classic design.
